            <p style="color: #475569; line-height: 1.6; text-align: justify;">
                This Non-Disclosure Agreement ("Agreement") is entered into as of the date set forth below between QOLAE (Quality of Life & Excellence) ("QOLAE" or "Disclosing Party") and <strong><%= reader.readerName %></strong> ("Reader" or "Receiving Party"). This Agreement governs the disclosure of confidential and proprietary information in connection with the Reader's engagement to review Immediate Needs Assessment (INA) reports and related documentation.
            </p>
        </div>

